title: Las Iguanas
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, Mexican, Brazilian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. UK chain Latin American food restaurant and bar serving dishes from Brazil and Mexico. Has labeled menu section for vegetarian and vegan food. Vegan options include mushroom fajita, salads, chilli, and a South American coconut based curry called bahia moqueca. Happy hour cocktails. Lively trendy atmosphere.
